snippet.title: Hunger Dungeon Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hunger Dungeon is Free-to-play on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/513560/

Purchase the Deluxe Edition to receive all 12 original Heroes and their alternate skins: http://store.steampowered.com/app/540330/

Hunger Dungeon is a 1-6 player round-based Multiplayer Online Battle Arena game with a special pixel art style. Battle with more than 12 unique characters in fast-paced Free-for-All and Team Deathmatch rounds. Or take on the challenging Dragon Mode - the exciting first PvE mode!

Follow Hunger Dungeon on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HungerDungeonEng

Follow Hunger Dungeon on Twitter: https://twitter.com/HungerDungeon
